data.description: This wonderful home offers comfort & convenience in a sought-after neighborhood. The property features 3 bedrooms & 1.5 bathrooms, with a semi-finished basement, making it perfect for a growing family. Kitchenette area and bonus room in the basement. With a living area of 2002 square feet, there is plenty of space for everyone to enjoy. Built in 1960, this home has a timeless appeal with its classic design & architecture. The interior is well-maintained & provides a cozy atmosphere for relaxation. The bedrooms are spacious & provide ample storage space. The bathrooms are clean & modern, offering both style & functionality. Built in 1960, this home has a timeless appeal with its classic design & architecture. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a wonderful home in a great location. Motvated Sellers!
